				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-44881af elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="44881af" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Revenue increased 5.7% YoY to AED 27.3 billion, driven by strong topline growth across both the Cover and Care segments. The performance in Q4 2025 was supported by the contribution from Hellenic Healthcare Group, which added AED 742 million to the Group revenue.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-2211" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="2" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-2211" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> <span style="font-size:19px;color:#878A92;padding-right:20px"> 02</span>16.1% Year-on-Year increase in EBITDA Performance </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none"><path d="M20.5389 11.0941L13.8173 4.13556L7.0957 11.0941" stroke="#878A92" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M13.8174 23.6239V4.33044" stroke="#878A92" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" id="Layer_1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 28 28" style="enable-background:new 0 0 28 28;" xml:space="preserve"><style type="text/css">	.st0{fill:none;stroke:#878A92;stroke-width:1.5;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-miterlimit:10;}</style><path class="st0" d="M7.1,16.7l6.7,7l6.7-7"></path><path class="st0" d="M13.8,4.1v19.3"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-2211" class="elementor-element elementor-element-edd4a62 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="edd4a62" data-element_type="container">
		<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-2211" class="elementor-element elementor-element-6f59838 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child" data-id="6f59838" data-element_type="container">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7648dfe elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="7648dfe" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>EBITDA grew 16.1% YoY to AED 4.8 billion, while the EBITDA Margin expanding by 1.6 ppts to 17.5%, reflecting strong operational excellence and disciplined cost management across both cover and care segments. Q4 2025 performance was further supported by Hellenic Healthcare Group, which contributed  AED 152 million to EBITDA at a strong margin of 20.5%, enhancing overall profitability.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-2212" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="3" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-2212" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> <span style="font-size:19px;color:#878A92;padding-right:20px"> 03</span> 17.7% Year-on-Year increase in net income </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none"><path d="M20.5389 11.0941L13.8173 4.13556L7.0957 11.0941" stroke="#878A92" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M13.8174 23.6239V4.33044" stroke="#878A92" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" id="Layer_1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 28 28" style="enable-background:new 0 0 28 28;" xml:space="preserve"><style type="text/css">	.st0{fill:none;stroke:#878A92;stroke-width:1.5;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-miterlimit:10;}</style><path class="st0" d="M7.1,16.7l6.7,7l6.7-7"></path><path class="st0" d="M13.8,4.1v19.3"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-2212" class="elementor-element elementor-element-e353a7f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="e353a7f" data-element_type="container">
		<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-2212" class="elementor-element elementor-element-b813605 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child" data-id="b813605" data-element_type="container">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a9352be elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="a9352be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Net Income rose 17.7% YoY to AED 2.0 billion, with the net income margin improving to 7.4%. This growth was achieved despite non-operational items and a higher tax rate of 15%, compared to 9% last year, following the implementation of Pillar Two tax requirements, highlighting exceptional performance within the Cover segment and enhanced operational efficiencies in the Care segment.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				</div>
					</details>
					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
